reviewText: This is one of the best Gaither Homecoming DVD's that I have purchased.  The music is very uplifting.  I loved seeing the Operation Christmas Child Shoeboxes actually being delivered by the Gaither Homecoming Friends.  I have made up shoeboxes for years and was very happy to see how much they are really loved and appreciated.  I would encourage everyone to do a shoebox for this very worthy cause.
